casebody.data:
First Department,

September, 1958

(September 10, 1958) In the Matter of the Arbitration between William V. Bradley, as President of the International Longshoremen’s Association, Ind., Appellant, and Grace Line Inc., Respondent.

Order unanimously affirmed, with $20 costs and disbursements to the respondent. No opinion. Concur — Botein, P. J., Rabin, Valente, McNally and Stevens, JJ.
